name: OscillatorNode.OscillatorNode
description: The OscillatorNode() constructor of the Web Audio API creates a new OscillatorNode object which is an AudioNode that represents a periodic waveform, like a sine wave, optionally setting the node's properties' values to match values in a specified object.
